<section class="bg-white section-padding">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-brand-red mx-auto"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">What is mobile pizza catering?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Mobile pizza catering brings our wood-fired pizza oven directly to your event location. We set up on-site and prepare fresh, authentic Neapolitan-style pizzas made to order for you and your guests.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">How does Bello Pizza work?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We arrive at your location with our mobile pizza oven, set up our station, and begin preparing fresh pizzas throughout your event. Our team handles all the cooking and service, allowing you to enjoy your event worry-free.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Is the Bello Pizza menu customizable?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Yes! We offer customizable menu options including various pizza styles, toppings, salads, meatballs, pasta, and wings. We can accommodate dietary restrictions and preferences to ensure all your guests are satisfied.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">What is the typical catering experience timeline?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We typically arrive 1-2 hours before service begins to set up and preheat our oven. Once ready, we can serve approximately 50-80 pizzas per hour, depending on the complexity of orders. Most events run for 2-4 hours of active service.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">What are your pricing and minimum requirements?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We have a 25-person minimum for all catering events. Our packages start at $18 per person for basic service and go up to $32 per person for our deluxe package. Travel fees may apply for events outside our standard service area.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">Do you accommodate dietary restrictions?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>Absolutely! We offer gluten-free dough options, vegan cheese, and can customize toppings to accommodate various dietary needs including vegetarian, vegan, and allergy restrictions. Please let us know your requirements when booking.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">What space do you need for setup?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We need approximately 20x20 feet of space for our mobile oven setup, with access to a standard electrical outlet. We can set up on grass, concrete, or asphalt. We'll work with you to find the best location at your venue.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-lg flex justify-between items-center">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">How far in advance should I book?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon text-2xl text-brand-red transform transition-transform">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer hidden p-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>We recommend booking at least 2-3 weeks in advance, especially for weekend events and during peak season (spring and summer). However, we can sometimes accommodate last-minute requests depending on our schedule.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item');
    
    faqItems.forEach(item => {
      const question = item.querySelector('.faq-question');
      const answer = item.querySelector('.faq-answer');
      const icon = item.querySelector('.faq-icon');
      
      question?.addEventListener('click', function() {
        const isOpen = !answer?.classList.contains('hidden');
        
        // Close all other FAQ items
        faqItems.forEach(otherItem => {
          if (otherItem !== item) {
            otherItem.querySelector('.faq-answer')?.classList.add('hidden');
            const otherIcon = otherItem.querySelector('.faq-icon');
            if (otherIcon) {
              otherIcon.textContent = '+';
              otherIcon.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
            }
          }
        });
        
        // Toggle current item
        if (isOpen) {
          answer?.classList.add('hidden');
          if (icon) {
            icon.textContent = '+';
            icon.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
          }
        } else {
          answer?.classList.remove('hidden');
          if (icon) {
            icon.textContent = 'âˆ’';
            icon.style.transform = 'rotate(180deg)';
          }
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>